00:26:01,375 --> 00:26:02,476
Apa semua ini?

356
00:26:02,476 --> 00:26:04,105
Kau sebelumnya mengerjakan tugasku juga, jadi kurasa...

357
00:26:04,105 --> 00:26:05,716
